            "title": "Cuaca hari ini",
            "titleEn": "Today's weather",
            "content": {
                "intro": "Learn to talk about weather in Indonesian. Indonesia has two main seasons: musim hujan (wet) and musim kemarau (dry).",
                "sentences": [
                    {
                        "id": "Hari ini cuaca akan cerah di pagi hari.",
                        "en": "Today the weather will be fine in the morning."
                    },
                    {
                        "id": "Hujan akan turun di sore hari.",
                        "en": "Rain will fall in the afternoon."
                    },
                    {
                        "id": "Disarankan untuk membawa payung.",
                        "en": "It is recommended to bring an umbrella."
                    }
                ],
                "grammar": {
                    "title": "Prepositions",
                    "explanation": "Key prepositions: **di** (at/in), **ke** (to), **dari** (from), **dalam** (inside), **luar** (outside), **atas** (above), **bawah** (below), **depan** (front), **belakang** (behind).",
                    "examples": [
                        {
                            "id": "di dalam ruangan",
                            "en": "indoors"
